  "ParseDate": "2024-10-11T14:01:38.8177069+03:00",
  "Content": "Conform unui sondaj recent realizat de Centrul de Investigații Sociologice și Marketing CBS-Axa, 63% dintre cetățenii Republicii Moldova sprijină aderarea țării la Uniunea Europeană, în creștere față de 57% în aprilie 2024. </strong> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-237996 size-full\" src=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-300x169.jpg 300w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-2000x1125.jpg 2000w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/459409446_885757899776453_663326269233989879_n-390x220.jpg 390w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"> Majoritatea respondenților consideră că cei care se opun integrării europene reprezintă o minoritate. Aproximativ 53% dintre cei chestionați cred că majoritatea populației susține aderarea la UE, în timp ce doar 32,6% cred contrariul, iar 15% rămân nehotărâți. <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-237997 size-full\" src=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-300x169.jpg 300w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-2000x1125.jpg 2000w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-390x220.jpg 390w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"> Majoritatea moldovenilor demonstrează reziliență în fața numeroaselor falsuri și manipulări menite să-i demotiveze de a participa la referendum. Majoritatea sunt hotărâți să meargă la vot pentru a decide obiectivul de dezvoltare strategică pe termen lung al țării. Dacă în luna august circa 66% de respondenți afirmau că vor merge și vor vota atât la prezidențiale cât și la referendum, iar circa 10% erau indeciși, în luna septembrie a scăzut numărul indecișilor cu 3,5%. Participarea la referendum și alegerile prezidențiale a crescut cu 2% și cam tot atât a crescut procentul celor care declară că vor participa doar la alegerile prezidențiale. <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-237998 size-full\" src=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-300x169.jpg 300w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-2000x1125.jpg 2000w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460114581_1085603343242239_5138055601518141973_n-390x220.jpg 390w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-237999 size-full\" src=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-300x169.jpg 300w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-2000x1125.jpg 2000w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/461701784_3380363975592018_7579931600314209697_n-390x220.jpg 390w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"> <em>Peste jumătate dintre cetățenii Republicii Moldova consideră că dezinformarea și manipularea opiniei publice de către actorii externi contribuie foarte mult la regresul din Republica Moldova</strong></em> Unul din mesajele toxice folosit de oponenții referendumului pentru a diviza societatea sugerează că diaspora nu trebuie să aibă dreptul să participe la referendum. <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-238000 size-full\" src=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-2000x1125.jpg 2000w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://zugo.md/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/460186248_1622033071988907_8921898524190335098_n-1-390x220.jpg 390w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"> "
